## Decision 025: Internal Normalized Definition Is Still Needed

Decision:
- Aim Brain still needs an internal validated format.
- This internal format can replace or refine the old BenchmarkPack type.

Reason:
- The engine needs stable structured data.
- Source adapters can handle messy external formats.

Status:
- locked

